@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gyfmae(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.45 / wp.sin(v1 + 0.55)) / wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.39)))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.21) / wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.79)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.94)) / v1)
    data[tid] = v0
